## 8. CODING STANDARDS

- TypeScript strict; explicit types on public interfaces
- Design tokens for ALL styling (/docs/10) — no magic colour values
- Handle empty states explicitly (e.g. "no antidote — supportive")
- Smallest change; comment WHY not what

## 10. DEFINITION OF DONE

- Acceptance criteria met
- Clinical values sourced + review-gated
- Tests passing (dosing/safety covered)
- Low-end Android / graceful offline where relevant
- No secrets; POPIA respected; constitution self-review
